high_descs: Turn left and walk across the kitchen to the black bin on the right
Pick up the tomato in the black bin
Turn around and walk across the kitchen to the sink on the left
Put the tomato in the sink next to the potato, fill the sink with water, drain the water from the sink, and pick up the tomato
Turn to the left and walk across the kitchen to the refrigerator on the right
Open the refrigerator door and put the tomato on the top shelf
anns.task_desc: Wash a tomato and put it in the refrigerator

high_descs: Walk to the left past the fridge and face the trash can on the floor.
Pick up the tomato out of the trash can.
Turn around and step toward the table, turn to the left and walk to the sink on your left.
Put the tomato in the sink, wash it, and pick it up.
Turn to the right and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the tomato on the shelf to the left of the the egg. Close the door.
anns.task_desc: Move a clean tomato to the fridge.

high_descs: Make a left to walk to the trash can to the left of the fridge.
Pick up the apple from the trash can.
Make a right to walk to the sink.
Wash the apple in the sink, removing it afterwards.
Turn left to walk to the fridge.
Put the apple in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Wash an apple to put in the fridge.
